\SE[5]It seems like we can go back to Ulyssean from here.
\!\SE[12]...For now, let's hurry ahead.

\SE[5]Welcome to Lunaroa's Dream... \!\SE[1]Even though I didn't
invite you...\.I'll still welcome you.

\SE\SE[23]The naughty child who created the entrance... well,
\SE[1]they were a bit troublesome, so I sent them to a different
place. \SE[23]Ahaha... But don't worry, they're fine for now, so
you can relax.

\SE\SE[1]I'll be waiting at the very back, so come quickly.
\!\SE[5]Oh, I've also prepared a cute helper for you, so make
sure to get along and cooperate properly. Got it? \!\SE[1]That's
all from me... Well then, see you.

\SE[74]...Since this is the enemy's territory, I guess we have no
choice but to play along with their make-believe. \!\SE[3]
\SE[17]I'm already prepared for resolve. Let's go.
